        "description": {
            "value": "<p>If the snare normally takes 1 minute to Craft, you can Craft it with 3 Interact actions instead. Each day during your daily preparations, you can prepare three snares from your formula book for quick deployment (increasing to four snares if you're a master in Crafting and five if you're legendary). Snares prepared in this way don't cost you any resources to Craft.</p>\n<p>When a creature critically fails its saving throw against and takes damage from the initial effect of a snare you Crafted and deployed, that creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Off-Guard] until the end of its next turn.</p>"
